description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=1/3, Sex=3/3, Mature Content=3/3. Play online with your avatar and immerse yourself in ridiculously awesome jet pack combat! Set on a lush island world you will get to blast your friends with your energy rocket launcher while soaring through the air and climbing the ranks on the global high scores list. Featuring 8 mind blistering jet pack songs provided by The Song Club.
